sources.description:
He's steer crazy! The whacky hacky with a meter that registered Laffs only! The trials and tribulations of a cab driver working the night shift, who must put with an assortment of crazies, hard-cases and sob-stories during work and then has to come home to a loud, argumentative, shrewish wife.

Original Title: Stop That Cab

Colorized version https://youtu.be/W3Li0up7xjo

Director: Eugenio de Liguoro
Writers: Walter Abbott, Louella MacFarlane
Stars: Sid Melton, Iris Adrian, Marjorie Lord, Tom Neal
Genres: Comedy, Crime
